snippet.title: Touchgrind Skate 2 - Official teaser
snippet.description:
Available for iOS on Apple App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/en/app/touchgrind-skate-2/id720068876?mt=8

Also available on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=se.illusionlabs.skate2&hl=en

This is the first preview of the upcoming Illusion Labs game Touchgrind Skate 2 - Real skateboarding in your pocket! Coming this year to the Apple App Store. 

Follow @ILLUSIONLABS on Twitter to get the latest news about this game!
